#: bitcaster/dispatchers/handlers/gmail.py:35
msgid ""
"Simplified Email dispatcher for GMail accounts.\n"
"\n"
"**Generate Application password**\n"
"\n"
"- Navigate to your [Google Account](https://myaccount.google.com/security).\n"
"- Under the Password & sign-in method section, click App passwords.\n"
"- If requested login again using your usual password.\n"
"- Make sure Other (custom name) is selected in the Select app drop-down "
"menu.\n"
" Type the application name (ie. Bitcaster)\n"
"- Click Generate.\n"
msgstr ""
"Dispatcher di e-mail semplificato per account GMail.\n"
"\n"
"** Genera password dell'applicazione **\n"
"\n"
"- Vai al tuo [Google Account](https://myaccount.google.com/security).\n"
"- Nella sezione Accesso a Google, fai clic su Password per le app.\n"
"- Se richiesto, effettuare di nuovo l'accesso utilizzando la normale "
"password.\n"
"- Assicurati che Altra (nome personalizzato) sia selezionato nel menu a "
"discesa Seleziona app.\n"
"Digita il nome dell'applicazione (es. Bitcaster)\n"
"- Clicca su Genera.\n"

#: bitcaster/dispatchers/handlers/hangout.py:100
msgid ""
"\n"
"#### Generate Application password\n"
"\n"
"- Navigate to your [Google Account](https://myaccount.google.com/security).\n"
"- Under the Password & sign-in method section, click App passwords.\n"
"- If requested login again using your usual password.\n"
"- Make sure Other (custom name) is selected in the Select app drop-down "
"menu.\n"
" Type the application name (ie. Bitcaster)\n"
"- Click Generate.\n"
"- Do not forget to check `Access for less secure app`\n"
msgstr ""

